timing_derate...eference_point(25.10)    timing_derate...eference_point(25.10)

Name
       timing_derate_ocv_reference_point

Syntax
       timing_derate_ocv_reference_point {1 | 0}

       Default: 1

       Allows  specification  of  reference  point for OCV factors. As per the
       current OCV library definitions, the OCV reference point is always  ex-
       pected to be set at 1.0.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

